node.text:
The Flying Spur and Bentayga have elevated the backseat entertainment experience. Do you...

🚘 - Get behind the wheel and take control of the V8 performance?
OR
😎- Enjoy the entertainment features of the backseat with your favourite film?
___

node.text:
The #FlyingSpur Hybrid represents more that just a car. It's a promise from us to you that we're on the road to becoming a leading sustainable luxury car company. All without compromising on comfort, power or performance. 
___

#Bentley #FlyingSpurHybrid is available to order in most markets, but is currently not available in EU27, UK, Switzerland, Israel, Ukraine, Norway, Turkey and Vietnam.

node.text:

From @JakeLingeman in @CarBuzz
